title: Seed
description:
This is the 2004 Special Edition with the following changes:





Greedo does not shoot Han. There was never a "first" shooter anyway.

On Darth Vader's first appearance, his leitmotif is heard as part of the music.

The end credits feature an alternate version of the music finale, matching the  credits in length but not using the amateurish, repetitive looping that was done with the John Williams score in all of the Special Edition releases.
